Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:13.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:17.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:22.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:27.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:31.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:40.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:50.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.89,0:24:59.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.11,0:25:08.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.37,0:25:16.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.35,0:25:17.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:23.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.83,0:25:25.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:13.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:17.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:22.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:27.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:31.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:40.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:50.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.89,0:24:59.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.11,0:25:08.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.37,0:25:16.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.35,0:25:17.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:23.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.83,0:25:25.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
